Hi, I'm from class 901, here's a leaflet for our stage play "Little Girl from the Accordion Star". Please come and take a look!
我是901班的，我这里有一份关于我们舞台剧《小风琴星人历险记》的表演介绍，请务必前来观看哦~
好的好的，看起来挺有意思的呢~
Ah, you guys came to help?
Great, we really need some more people right now
太好了，我们现在真的很缺人手
There are some leaflets for our stage performance, can one of you help me to hand them out?
这里有些宣传我们班舞台剧表演的传单，你们两位看看能不能有一位帮我发一下？
只要发出去五张就可以了！
No WangMilk San, you need to stay here and man this booth with me
王缪可同学你可能需要留下来帮我看着一下摊位
It's fine WangMilk, I can do it by myself. You can stay
没事王缪可，我来就好，你去帮她忙吧
May Chyan, what was going on just now?
Ah, you are back! So fast! Shiro San said Ari San fell over in the gym, and they need someone to help her immediately…
啊你回来了，这么快！刚才小白同学跑过来说雅莉同学在体育馆那边摔倒了，所以需要立刻找个人过去帮忙…
Yes, the girl with glasses, she sits in the corner and doesn't like to talk a lot
嗯，就是在班里不太经常说话，戴着眼镜坐在角落的那位
I tried to talk to her a few times but she didn't respond to me…
我有几次想和她说话她都不理我…
Ahh, I know who you are talking about
(The one who didn't talk to me in the morning, right?)
(就是早上的时候没有回我话的那一位嘛？)
(Wait why did I not know that until now?)
Yes, I also heard that Ari San has some health issues. I heard that she has anemia…
嗯，我听说雅莉同学身体不太好，听说好像是有一点贫血…
希望她没出什么大问题…
Yeah… I hope everyone can be well
是啊…希望大家都能健康
(Shy… hahaha, I'm also a bit shy too…)
(怕生…哈哈哈，可能我自己也是呢…)
(Although other people may not know, I'm always feeling stressed out when I need to talk to a stranger...)
(虽然别人可能看不出来，可是我和不认识的人说话的时候，压力也挺大的……)
But don't worry, Takuya was asked to go and help them out, we should also finish our business here
没事，王缪可已经过去帮忙了，我们也要把我们这边的事情做好才行
Ah, so you have finished handing out your leaflets, right? Amazing!
啊你已经发完传单了？太快了！
I had been trying for the whole morning but only managed to give out 3, you are just amazing!
我可是发了一早上都没发出去超过3张，你太厉害了！
Here's 15 more, can you help me to give them out please??
来，这里还有15张，你继续帮我发一发吧，可以拜托你吗？？
Jes… I was forced to distribute at least 50 leaflets this morning…
天…结果一上午被逼着发了50多张传单…
Anyway, it's lunch time now, I should go to the store on the first floor to buy some lunch~
还好，午饭时间到了，去一楼小卖部买个午饭吧~
